context:
KR:
&lt;여기도 엄청 크네… 이곳에서 계속 혼자 지냈던 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;This place is huge, too… You’ve been living here alone all along?&gt;

KR:
&lt;아, 이분이…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Oh hey, is she—?&gt;

KR:
&lt;지금까지 준비해 왔던 것이라면… 가시춘이 계속 말했던…&gt;
EN:
&lt;What the descendants have prepared, huh... So this must be what Jia Xichun's been referring to this whole time...&gt;

KR:
&lt;그래서 진정한 불로불사에 대한 답이 뭔데…?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Right, so… what’s the answer to true immortality, then...?&gt;

KR:
&lt;아, 음… 금방 돌아왔네?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Hey, uhm... you're back pretty soon, huh.&gt;

KR:
&lt;홍루, 방금 말은… 걸러 들어도 돼.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Hong Lu, you don’t have to… don’t mind what she just said.&gt;

KR:
&lt;쓰임새…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Your 'use'...&gt;

KR:
&lt;…사이가 다시 좋아지고 싶다거나 그런 건 없어?&gt;
EN:
&lt;But… don’t you want to be friends with her again?&gt;

KR:
&lt;홍루… 혹시 가주 대전에 나가는 것에 대해서도…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Hong Lu, about participating in the Family Hierarch war...&gt;

KR:
&lt;너의 마음은 아예 배제하고 있는 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;... do you really not feel anything about it? Have you completely excluded yourself from it?&gt;

KR:
&lt;…….&gt;
EN:
&lt;…….&gt;

KR:
&lt;출발까진 시간이 좀 남았네.&gt;
EN:
&lt;There's still some time until we have to leave.&gt;

KR:
&lt;명령한 적은 없어…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Hey, I didn't even give an order...&gt;
